  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Integrated Payment systems give users a secure solution for accepting payments on a payment terminal and seamlessly posting those transactions to a RepairQ ticket. This streamlines the checkout process and reduces accounting errors compared to manually recording payments.</p><p>RepairQ offers integrated payment processing through the following providers:</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.bluefinpartner.com/repairq/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluefin Payment Systems</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://squareup.com/signup?country_code=us&amp;signup_token=5193B6FB67\" rel=\"nofollow\">Square Payments</a></p></li></ul><p>Bluefin integration is currently available for customers in the United States, and Square is available in the United States and Canada. Their\u00a0devices support Europay, MasterCard, Visa (<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://repairq.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/236101628\" rel=\"nofollow\">EMV</a>), and Point-to-Point Encryption (<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.bluefin.com/products/p2pe-point-to-point-encryption/\" rel=\"nofollow\">P2PE</a>) payment processing for secure and reliable payment processing.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295157/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-IntegratedPaymentInformation\">Integrated Payment Information</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934786770/Integrated+Payments+Supported+Devices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934786770\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Supported Integrated Payment Devices</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917825/EMV+Frequently+Asked+Questions+-+FAQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934917825\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">EMV Frequently Asked Questions - FAQ</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1938030595/Integrated+Payments+Square+and+Afterpay\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1938030595\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments: Square and Afterpay</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-ActivatingYourBluefinDevice\">Activating Your Bluefin Device</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934786801/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Activate+Your+P2PE+Device\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934786801\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Activate Your P2PE Device</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917867\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934917867\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917867</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229806/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Configuring+a+Bluefin+PAX+A80+A920+to+Communicate+with+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229806\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Configuring a Bluefin PAX A80 to Communicate with RepairQ</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934196887/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Configuring+a+Bluefin+PAX+D210+to+Communicate+with+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934196887\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Configuring a Bluefin PAX D210 to Communicate with RepairQ</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-PaymentIntegrationSet-upinRepairQ\">Payment Integration Set-up in RepairQ</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934786847/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Adding+Bluefin+Credentials+in+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934786847\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Adding Bluefin Integration Credentials in RepairQ</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936556034/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Activating+Square+Integration+in+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936556034\" data-linked-resource-version=\"15\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Activating Square Integration in RepairQ</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-InstallingtheSecurityCertificate(BluefinOnly)\">Installing the Security Certificate (Bluefin Only)</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934786687/Integrated+Payments+Setup+PAX+Security+Certificate+Installation+and+Testing\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934786687\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: PAX Security Certificate Installation</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-AddingPaymentDevicestoRepairQ\">Adding Payment Devices to RepairQ</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1935376416/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Adding+a+Bluefin+PAX+Payment+Terminal+Device+in+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1935376416\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Adding a Bluefin PAX Payment Terminal Device in RepairQ</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936588814/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Add+a+Square+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936588814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Adding a Square Payment Device in RepairQ</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-ProcessingPayments\">Processing Payments</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Starting a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936785459/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Assigning+a+Square+Terminal+to+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936785459\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Assigning a Square Terminal to a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1935507459/Integrated+Payment+Setup+Assigning+Your+PAX+Payment+Device+to+a+VCT+and+Processing+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1935507459\" data-linked-resource-version=\"15\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payment Setup: Assigning Your PAX to a VCT and Processing Payments</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1935179832/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Assigning+Your+IDTECH+SREDKey+to+a+VCT+and+Processing+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1935179832\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Assigning Your IDTECH SREDKey to a VCT and Processing Payments</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936719893/Integrated+Payments+Accepting+Payments+on+a+Square+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936719893\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments: Accepting Payments with a Square Terminal</a></p><h2 id=\"IntegratedPaymentProcessing-StartHere!-Troubleshooting\">Troubleshooting</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229721/Integrated+Payments+Troubleshooting+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229721\" data-linked-resource-version=\"19\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments: Connectivity Troubleshooting Resources</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1938161692/PAX+Device+Troubleshooting+Duplicate+Payment+Requests\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1938161692\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PAX Device Troubleshooting: Duplicate Payment Requests</a> </p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1935769605/Integrated+Payments+Setup+Performing+a+Test+Transaction+with+a+PAX+Terminal+Device\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1935769605\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payments Setup: Performing a Test Transaction with a PAX Terminal Device</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937014916/PAX+Device+Troubleshooting+Invalid+Credit+Card+Entry\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937014916\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PAX Device Troubleshooting: Invalid Credit Card Entry</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934197020/PAX+Device+Troubleshooting+Update+Your+IP+Address+in+RepairQ\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934197020\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Payment Devices: Updating Your IP Address in RepairQ</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
